message.content:
Theory

Explanation: The paper describes modifications to the Structure-Mapping Engine (SME) algorithm to make it more efficient and relevant to an analogizer's goals. It does not use any specific sub-category of AI such as Case Based, Genetic Algorithms, Neural Networks, Probabilistic Methods, Reinforcement Learning, or Rule Learning. Instead, it focuses on theoretical analysis and modifications to an existing algorithm. Therefore, the paper belongs to the sub-category of AI called Theory.
